WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:00.900
[THEME MUSIC]
THEME SONG: Let's go!

00:00.900 --> 00:01.600
Peter Rabbit.

00:01.600 --> 00:03.590
Go on a run.

00:03.590 --> 00:05.660
Run for our lives.

00:05.660 --> 00:08.590
We'll tear a hole in every
fence and every wall.

00:08.590 --> 00:09.290
Peter Rabbit.

00:09.290 --> 00:10.420
Run through the fields.

00:10.420 --> 00:11.120
[HOOTING]

00:11.120 --> 00:13.380
Run wild and free.

00:13.380 --> 00:16.040
And grab a piece of
every radish that we see.

00:16.040 --> 00:16.740
Peter Rabbit.

00:16.740 --> 00:18.710
Go day and night.

00:18.710 --> 00:20.680
Go for it all.

00:20.680 --> 00:21.660
It's time to fly.

00:21.660 --> 00:22.650
Come on.

00:22.650 --> 00:23.920
The wind's begun to blow.

00:23.920 --> 00:24.620
Let's go!

00:24.620 --> 00:27.570
'Cause you and I, we
weren't made for going slow.

00:27.570 --> 00:28.550
Let's go!

00:28.550 --> 00:29.290
Adventure calls.

00:29.290 --> 00:30.310
The game is on.

00:30.310 --> 00:31.010
Come on!

00:31.010 --> 00:31.710
Let's go!

00:31.710 --> 00:32.490
Peter Rabbit!

00:32.490 --> 00:33.470
Let's go!

00:33.470 --> 00:34.460
Peter Rabbit!

00:34.460 --> 00:35.440
Let's go!

00:35.440 --> 00:36.220
Peter Rabbit!

00:36.220 --> 00:36.920
Let's go!

00:40.360 --> 00:42.330
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:43.340 --> 00:45.220
PETER RABBIT ( VOICEOVER):
"The Tale of the Lying Fox."

00:51.430 --> 00:52.420
[SNORING]

00:52.420 --> 00:53.420
[CLUNK]

00:54.900 --> 00:56.890
[SNIFFING]

00:58.870 --> 01:00.860
[GROWLING]

01:00.860 --> 01:02.340
Meow!

01:02.340 --> 01:04.330
[INTENSE MUSIC]

01:08.300 --> 01:10.280
[MEOWING]

01:15.240 --> 01:16.230
[GRUNTING]

01:16.230 --> 01:17.720
Coming through.

01:17.720 --> 01:20.200
Oh!

01:20.200 --> 01:21.190
[GROWLING]

01:31.110 --> 01:33.590
[MEOWING]

01:33.590 --> 01:35.080
[DEFEATED MEOW]

01:36.360 --> 01:37.060
Yes!

01:43.310 --> 01:44.009
[GRUNTS]

01:44.009 --> 01:45.990
MR. TOD: [GROANING]

01:45.990 --> 01:46.780
Now what?

01:50.150 --> 01:51.320
[SNIFFING]

01:51.320 --> 01:53.460
Oh, stupid fencing.

01:53.460 --> 01:54.160
[GRUNTING]

01:54.160 --> 01:56.280
Uh, Mr. Tod?

01:56.280 --> 01:58.080
What are you doing here?

01:58.080 --> 02:01.280
What does it look like I'm
doing, you ridiculous rabbit?

02:01.280 --> 02:02.900
I'm hunting.

02:02.900 --> 02:03.600
What?

02:03.600 --> 02:04.830
Strawberries?

02:04.830 --> 02:05.990
No.

02:05.990 --> 02:06.690
You!

02:06.690 --> 02:09.530
[GROWLS] Ow!

02:09.530 --> 02:11.860
My paw!

02:11.860 --> 02:13.780
You want to watch
out for that fencing.

02:13.780 --> 02:14.770
It's tricky.

02:14.770 --> 02:16.610
MR. MCGREGOR: [WHISTLING]

02:19.600 --> 02:21.190
[GASPS] Mr. McGregor!

02:21.190 --> 02:23.650
Well, it's been nice
talking with you Mr. Tod,

02:23.650 --> 02:25.020
but I'm afraid I've
got to hop to it.

02:25.020 --> 02:25.720
Wait!

02:25.720 --> 02:27.820
Peter, don't leave me.

02:27.820 --> 02:30.040
Mr. McGregor hates foxes.

02:30.040 --> 02:34.460
I'll be stuffed and put on
the mantelpiece for sure.

02:34.460 --> 02:39.260
Your-- your father wouldn't
let a fellow creature out here.

02:39.260 --> 02:40.690
What did you say?

02:40.690 --> 02:44.470
I said, yo-- your father
wouldn't have left me out here.

02:44.470 --> 02:45.670
He'd have helped.

02:45.670 --> 02:47.630
[INTENSE MUSIC]

02:47.630 --> 02:51.100
[SIGHS] I can't believe I'm
even thinking of helping Mr.

02:51.100 --> 02:54.050
Tod.

02:54.050 --> 02:58.260
If I help you, do you promise
you won't try to catch me?

02:58.260 --> 03:01.820
No, but I'll give
you a head start.

03:01.820 --> 03:02.520
All right.

03:02.520 --> 03:03.360
All right.

03:03.360 --> 03:05.480
Rabbit is off my menu for good.

03:05.480 --> 03:07.020
Fox's honour.

03:07.020 --> 03:08.860
Just get me out of here.

03:08.860 --> 03:09.810
Hurry!

03:09.810 --> 03:12.220
MR. MCGREGOR: [WHISTLING]

03:12.220 --> 03:13.180
[RATTLING]

03:13.180 --> 03:16.550
[GRUNTING]

03:16.550 --> 03:19.440
[CHUCKLES] Silly rabbit.

03:19.440 --> 03:23.120
Never turn your back on a fox.

03:23.120 --> 03:24.100
Ouch!

03:24.100 --> 03:26.520
My paw!

03:26.520 --> 03:27.840
Shh!

03:27.840 --> 03:31.570
If you want to get out of
here, you've got to be quiet.

03:31.570 --> 03:32.940
Come on!

03:32.940 --> 03:35.550
MR. MCGREGOR: What's
going on over here?

03:35.550 --> 03:36.800
Oh no.

03:36.800 --> 03:41.690
[GRUMBLING] I know you're in
here somewhere, you thieves!

03:41.690 --> 03:44.060
[GRUNTING] Ow.

03:44.060 --> 03:44.760
Oof.

03:44.760 --> 03:45.460
Ow.

03:45.460 --> 03:48.180
It's a dead end,
you foolish rabbit.

03:48.180 --> 03:49.500
You say dead end.

03:49.500 --> 03:50.710
I say clever escape route.

03:50.710 --> 03:51.410
Look!

03:54.210 --> 03:56.579
Even a one-legged fox
should be able to climb

03:56.579 --> 03:58.240
up there and over the wall.

03:58.240 --> 04:00.490
[GROANING]

04:01.380 --> 04:02.850
You could say thank you.

04:02.850 --> 04:05.130
Say thank you to a rabbit?

04:05.130 --> 04:05.910
Pah!

04:05.910 --> 04:08.140
I'd rather eat this cane here.

04:08.140 --> 04:10.610
Whoa!

04:10.610 --> 04:12.100
Ouch!

04:12.100 --> 04:14.070
Ooh.

04:14.070 --> 04:15.060
[SIGHS]

04:17.040 --> 04:18.950
Thank you.

04:18.950 --> 04:22.100
MR. MCGREGOR: Don't think
I can't hear you, rabbits!

04:22.100 --> 04:24.290
[GASPS] Mr. McGregor!

04:24.290 --> 04:27.270
You've got to help me find
another way out of here.

04:27.270 --> 04:28.190
Please.

04:28.190 --> 04:29.750
If you do, I'll--

04:29.750 --> 04:33.830
I'll-- I'll give you all the
vegetables in my kitchen.

04:33.830 --> 04:35.650
MR. MCGREGOR: Come
back here, rabbits!

04:35.650 --> 04:37.070
All of them?

04:37.070 --> 04:38.520
OK, fine.

04:38.520 --> 04:41.210
But follow me and stay low.

04:41.210 --> 04:43.670
The only vegetables
you're going to see

04:43.670 --> 04:45.800
are the ones cooking
with you in my pot.

04:45.800 --> 04:47.310
MR. MCGREGOR: Come back here!

04:47.310 --> 04:48.010
Wait!

04:48.010 --> 04:48.710
Wait!

04:48.710 --> 04:49.760
N-- N-- Not so fast!

04:49.760 --> 04:52.000
[GROANING] Ouch!

04:52.000 --> 04:52.900
Oh!

04:52.900 --> 04:54.900
My paw.

04:54.900 --> 04:56.040
Wait!

04:56.040 --> 04:59.150
Just keep up Mr. Tod,
or I'll end up in a pie,

04:59.150 --> 05:02.460
and you'll end up as a fur hat.

05:02.460 --> 05:04.880
[MUSIC PLAYING] (SINGING)
Stand your ground.

05:04.880 --> 05:06.620
You got no time to get away.

05:09.960 --> 05:11.370
You can't just run.

05:11.370 --> 05:13.330
This game is all or none.

05:13.330 --> 05:17.460
You've got to use your
wits to get you through.

05:17.460 --> 05:19.760
I know you're going to
figure out what to do.

05:19.760 --> 05:21.670
[HOWLS]

05:24.290 --> 05:25.300
Oh, I hate snails.

05:27.860 --> 05:28.560
Perfect.

05:32.030 --> 05:33.510
This will do it.

05:37.470 --> 05:38.470
Ooh!

05:38.470 --> 05:39.240
Ouch!

05:39.240 --> 05:40.130
Ooh!

05:40.130 --> 05:41.480
Ooh!

05:41.480 --> 05:42.270
Ouch!

05:42.270 --> 05:42.970
Hm.

05:42.970 --> 05:43.890
Next plan.

05:43.890 --> 05:44.790
[CHUCKLES]

05:46.600 --> 05:47.500
MR. TOD: Oh!

05:47.500 --> 05:51.740
A little higher, or I'll be
trapped in this garden forever.

05:51.740 --> 05:54.330
PETER RABBIT: Stop complaining.

05:54.330 --> 05:55.800
[GRUNTING]

05:55.800 --> 05:56.770
[MEOWS]

05:56.770 --> 05:57.750
Ah!

05:57.750 --> 05:58.730
Cat!

05:58.730 --> 06:01.660
[WHINING]

06:01.660 --> 06:04.110
[CAT GROWLING]

06:04.110 --> 06:04.840
Ooh.

06:04.840 --> 06:05.830
[INTENSE MUSIC]

06:05.830 --> 06:06.600
[GRUNTING]

06:07.300 --> 06:08.290
[PANTING]

06:09.760 --> 06:12.220
[GROWLING]

06:12.220 --> 06:13.700
[GASPS] Dead end!

06:13.700 --> 06:15.670
[MEOWING]

06:16.950 --> 06:17.650
Ha!

06:17.650 --> 06:19.270
Take that, cat.

06:19.270 --> 06:20.260
[CAT MEOWS]

06:20.260 --> 06:22.310
That was a nice move.

06:22.310 --> 06:24.020
Oh, you think?

06:24.020 --> 06:26.880
Well, thanks very much.

06:26.880 --> 06:28.800
Wait a second.

06:28.800 --> 06:30.460
Why did you help me?

06:30.460 --> 06:33.190
I took no pleasure
in it, believe me.

06:33.190 --> 06:37.780
But with my injured paw, I
can't just hop over the wall.

06:37.780 --> 06:41.380
I still need your help to get
me out of this accursed garden.

06:41.380 --> 06:42.890
[CAT MEOWING]

06:42.890 --> 06:44.870
Uh, I don't know, Mr. Tod.

06:44.870 --> 06:45.870
I should get going.

06:45.870 --> 06:46.710
No!

06:46.710 --> 06:48.370
Y-you can't leave.

06:48.370 --> 06:49.330
Please, Peter.

06:49.330 --> 06:50.520
Help me, and I'll--

06:50.520 --> 06:53.470
I'll, um-- I'll show
you where to find

06:53.470 --> 06:56.650
my secret blackberry bush.

06:56.650 --> 06:58.750
I already know what that is.

06:58.750 --> 07:00.300
You do?

07:00.300 --> 07:01.060
All right, then.

07:01.060 --> 07:04.940
I promise not to try and
catch you while you eat them.

07:04.940 --> 07:06.760
[SIGHS] OK, Mr. Tod.

07:06.760 --> 07:09.500
Follow me, and try to keep up.

07:09.500 --> 07:10.360
Hah!

07:10.360 --> 07:13.120
Won't try to catch you, indeed.

07:13.120 --> 07:14.470
Foolish rabbit.

07:14.470 --> 07:17.290
Have I got a surprise
in store for you.

07:17.290 --> 07:18.750
[GROWLING]

07:20.690 --> 07:21.660
[GROWLS]

07:21.660 --> 07:23.120
[MEOWS]

07:23.120 --> 07:24.580
Ooh!

07:24.580 --> 07:25.430
Ow!

07:25.430 --> 07:27.320
[MUSIC PLAYING]

07:32.210 --> 07:35.070
Oh sweet, sweet freedom.

07:35.070 --> 07:35.880
Whoa there.

07:35.880 --> 07:36.580
Look.

07:36.580 --> 07:38.310
MR. MCGREGOR: [WHISTLING]

07:44.130 --> 07:45.840
If you get me
out of the garden,

07:45.840 --> 07:49.080
I promise I'll never chase
you or any of your friends,

07:49.080 --> 07:50.560
ever again.

07:50.560 --> 07:53.130
And don't forget all the
vegetables in your kitchen.

07:53.130 --> 07:54.960
And the secret blackberry bush.

07:54.960 --> 07:56.880
Yes, yes, you can have it all.

07:56.880 --> 07:57.970
Fox's honour.

07:57.970 --> 08:00.460
Just get me out of here.

08:00.460 --> 08:01.160
OK.

08:01.160 --> 08:02.470
Wait here.

08:02.470 --> 08:04.230
[SHOVELLING]

08:04.960 --> 08:05.660
Hmph.

08:05.660 --> 08:07.180
Fox's honour.

08:07.180 --> 08:10.330
[CHUCKLES] Not likely.

08:10.330 --> 08:13.190
MR. MCGREGOR: (SINGING)
I like rabbits in a pot.

08:13.190 --> 08:14.380
Potatoes.

08:14.380 --> 08:15.920
Peas.

08:15.920 --> 08:17.540
Nice and hot.

08:17.540 --> 08:19.500
[LAUGHS]

08:24.890 --> 08:27.840
Wait!

08:27.840 --> 08:30.040
You're going to have to
be quick this time, Peter.

08:30.040 --> 08:31.770
Really quick.

08:31.770 --> 08:33.250
[GRUNTS]

08:36.200 --> 08:38.659
[PANTING]

08:38.659 --> 08:40.630
[GRUNTING]

08:48.010 --> 08:48.950
[WATER SPRAYING]

08:48.950 --> 08:49.650
MR. MCGREGOR: Help!

08:49.650 --> 08:50.350
Help!

08:50.350 --> 08:52.450
It's spraying water!

08:52.450 --> 08:54.490
What are you waiting for?

08:54.490 --> 08:55.910
Hop to it.

08:55.910 --> 08:57.720
Well, hobble to it, anyway.

09:04.660 --> 09:06.050
You're a smart rabbit.

09:06.050 --> 09:07.280
I'll give you that.

09:07.280 --> 09:11.390
MR. MCGREGOR: I can hear
you, you wee rascals.

09:11.390 --> 09:12.650
[DOOR CLOSES]

09:12.650 --> 09:13.350
[GASPS]

09:13.350 --> 09:16.610
But not smart enough.

09:16.610 --> 09:17.490
[EVIL LAUGHING]

09:17.490 --> 09:18.190
No!

09:18.190 --> 09:19.260
Open it!

09:19.260 --> 09:21.190
Do you know the
other thing your father

09:21.190 --> 09:23.160
would never have done, Peter?

09:23.160 --> 09:26.740
He'd have never trusted a fox.

09:26.740 --> 09:27.710
[SNICKERING]

09:27.710 --> 09:29.670
You lied!

09:29.670 --> 09:30.720
What can I say?

09:30.720 --> 09:32.100
I'm a fox.

09:32.100 --> 09:34.260
I confess I've always
wanted to catch you,

09:34.260 --> 09:37.380
Peter, but it seems I must leave
that honour to Mr. McGregor.

09:37.380 --> 09:38.160
[GASPS]

09:38.160 --> 09:40.230
I imagine he'd
rather enjoy you--

09:40.230 --> 09:41.510
in a pie.

09:41.510 --> 09:43.630
[LAUGHS] Cheerio.

09:43.630 --> 09:45.080
[GRUNTING]

09:45.080 --> 09:47.490
[LAUGHING]

09:47.490 --> 09:50.700
[GRUNTING]

09:50.700 --> 09:51.930
MR. MCGREGOR:
You're mine, rabbit!

09:51.930 --> 09:52.910
Oh, no!

09:58.780 --> 10:00.240
MR. MCGREGOR: Stop, rabbit!

10:00.240 --> 10:04.640
Not today, you won't!

10:04.640 --> 10:06.110
[CAT MEOWING]

10:08.070 --> 10:11.710
MR. MCGREGOR: Away,
you wretched cat!

10:11.710 --> 10:13.420
One of dad's secret tunnels.

10:20.930 --> 10:22.370
[RUFFLING]

10:22.370 --> 10:26.570
MR. TOD: I can't believe he fell
for the old fox's honour lie.

10:26.570 --> 10:29.690
[CHUCKLES] Stupid rabbit.

10:29.690 --> 10:32.570
That's the last time
you tricked me, Mr. Tod.

10:32.570 --> 10:34.200
Two can play at that game.

10:34.200 --> 10:34.900
Hm.

10:38.320 --> 10:40.270
Yes, I'm out!

10:40.270 --> 10:42.170
Peter Rabbit?

10:42.170 --> 10:44.790
Oh, I should have
known you'd get away.

10:44.790 --> 10:46.350
PETER RABBIT: Mr. Tod!

10:46.350 --> 10:47.050
Help me!

10:47.050 --> 10:48.580
I'm stuck inside the tunnel!

10:48.580 --> 10:51.060
Oh, I'll help all right.

10:51.060 --> 10:52.670
Help eat you up.

10:52.670 --> 10:53.370
[RUSHING SOUND]

10:53.370 --> 10:55.360
What on earth?

10:55.360 --> 10:56.060
[WATER SPRAYING]

10:56.060 --> 10:58.130
PETER RABBIT: [LAUGHING]

10:58.130 --> 10:58.830
Oh!

10:58.830 --> 10:59.530
No!

10:59.530 --> 11:01.650
My jacket!

11:01.650 --> 11:03.340
I just got this
tailored, you know.

11:03.340 --> 11:04.300
Oh, stop it.

11:04.300 --> 11:05.760
Stop it.

11:05.760 --> 11:06.460
Oh!

11:06.460 --> 11:07.860
Come back here.

11:07.860 --> 11:11.530
[GRUNTING] Wait, Peter, help me.

11:11.530 --> 11:13.630
I'll do whatever you say.

11:13.630 --> 11:16.930
I should have known better
than to trust a lying fox.

11:16.930 --> 11:18.440
Goodbye, Mr. Tod.

11:18.440 --> 11:20.170
I'm going home.

11:20.170 --> 11:22.560
[GRUNTING] Wait!

11:25.100 --> 11:26.490
Hello?

11:26.490 --> 11:27.190
Hello?

11:30.190 --> 11:31.390
[CRICKETS CHIRPING]

11:32.890 --> 11:34.990
Help?

11:34.990 --> 11:36.340
[OWL HOOTING]

11:36.340 --> 11:38.590
Help!

11:38.590 --> 11:39.390
[SIGHS]

11:39.390 --> 11:40.090
[THEME MUSIC]

11:40.090 --> 11:41.290
THEME SONG: Peter Rabbit!

11:52.090 --> 11:53.890
Peter Rabbit!

11:53.890 --> 11:55.990
Peter Rabbit!

11:55.990 --> 11:58.140
Peter Rabbit!
